RE: How can the universe be uncaused? Holy crap, I was posting my question to you in the other thread as you were posting this. Devine intervention? Lol, just messin with ya.
My answer is simple. I don't know. Not knowing doesn't justify me filling in my gap of knowledge with something made up. So I accept that until I see solid evidence of whether the universe can come to be with, or without a cause, I just won't know.
